<Link id="l00433" /><CodeLine lineNumber="433"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeyword">static</span><span class="doxyHighlight"> </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeyword">const</span><span class="doxyHighlight"> int8&#95;t NoopsInSledCount = 7;</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00434" /><CodeLine lineNumber="434"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// We want to emit the following pattern:</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00435" /><CodeLine lineNumber="435"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00436" /><CodeLine lineNumber="436"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// .Lxray&#95;sled&#95;N:</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00437" /><CodeLine lineNumber="437"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//   ALIGN</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00438" /><CodeLine lineNumber="438"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//   B #32</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00439" /><CodeLine lineNumber="439"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//   ; 7 NOP instructions (28 bytes)</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00440" /><CodeLine lineNumber="440"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// .tmpN</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00441" /><CodeLine lineNumber="441"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00442" /><CodeLine lineNumber="442"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// We need the 28 bytes (7 instructions) because at runtime, we&#39;d be patching</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00443" /><CodeLine lineNumber="443"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// over the full 32 bytes (8 instructions) with the following pattern:</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00444" /><CodeLine lineNumber="444"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00445" /><CodeLine lineNumber="445"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//   STP X0, X30, &#91;SP, #-16&#93;! ; push X0 and the link register to the stack</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00446" /><CodeLine lineNumber="446"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//   LDR W17, #12 ; W17 := function ID</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00447" /><CodeLine lineNumber="447"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//   LDR X16,#12 ; X16 := addr of &#95;&#95;xray&#95;FunctionEntry or &#95;&#95;xray&#95;FunctionExit</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00448" /><CodeLine lineNumber="448"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//   BLR X16 ; call the tracing trampoline</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00449" /><CodeLine lineNumber="449"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//   ;DATA: 32 bits of function ID</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00450" /><CodeLine lineNumber="450"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//   ;DATA: lower 32 bits of the address of the trampoline</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00451" /><CodeLine lineNumber="451"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//   ;DATA: higher 32 bits of the address of the trampoline</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00452" /><CodeLine lineNumber="452"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//   LDP X0, X30, &#91;SP&#93;, #16 ; pop X0 and the link register from the stack</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00453" /><CodeLine lineNumber="453"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00454" /><CodeLine lineNumber="454"><span class="doxyHighlight">  <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/asmprinter/#ac189a157a6aab76ea837c13ec615dbc9">OutStreamer</a>-&gt;emitCodeAlignment(<a href="/docs/api/structs/llvm/align">Align</a>(4), &amp;<a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/asmprinter/#aebe7e48735a59049062e384e810c108a">getSubtargetInfo</a>());</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00455" /><CodeLine lineNumber="455"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeyword">auto</span><span class="doxyHighlight"> CurSled = <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/asmprinter/#aa7625af893e242d33b9f182066f59310">OutContext</a>.createTempSymbol(</span><span class="doxyHighlightStringLiteral">&quot;xray&#95;sled&#95;&quot;</span><span class="doxyHighlight">, </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeyword">true</span><span class="doxyHighlight">);</span></CodeLine>

<Link id="l00462" /><CodeLine lineNumber="462"><span class="doxyHighlight">  <a href="/docs/api/classes/anonymous-namespace-aarch64asmprinter-cpp-/aarch64asmprinter/#ad227b3ae621f2b01c29ad057c72348e3">EmitToStreamer</a>(&#42;<a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/asmprinter/#ac189a157a6aab76ea837c13ec615dbc9">OutStreamer</a>, <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/mcinstbuilder">MCInstBuilder</a>(AArch64::B).addImm(8));</span></CodeLine>

<Link id="l02347" /><CodeLine lineNumber="2347"></CodeLine>
<Link id="l02348" /><CodeLine lineNumber="2348"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// Emit:</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l02349" /><CodeLine lineNumber="2349"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// target materialization:</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l02350" /><CodeLine lineNumber="2350"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// - via GOT:</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l02351" /><CodeLine lineNumber="2351"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//   - unsigned GOT:</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l02352" /><CodeLine lineNumber="2352"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//       adrp x16, :got:target</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l02353" /><CodeLine lineNumber="2353"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//       ldr x16, &#91;x16, :got&#95;lo12:target&#93;</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l02354" /><CodeLine lineNumber="2354"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//       add offset to x16 if offset != 0</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l02355" /><CodeLine lineNumber="2355"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//   - ELF signed GOT:</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l02356" /><CodeLine lineNumber="2356"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//       adrp x17, :got:target</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l02357" /><CodeLine lineNumber="2357"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//       add x17, x17, :got&#95;auth&#95;lo12:target</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l02358" /><CodeLine lineNumber="2358"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//       ldr x16, &#91;x17&#93;</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l02359" /><CodeLine lineNumber="2359"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//       aut&#123;i|d&#125;a x16, x17</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l02360" /><CodeLine lineNumber="2360"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//       check+trap sequence (if no FPAC)</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l02361" /><CodeLine lineNumber="2361"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//       add offset to x16 if offset != 0</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l02362" /><CodeLine lineNumber="2362"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l02363" /><CodeLine lineNumber="2363"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// - direct:</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l02364" /><CodeLine lineNumber="2364"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//     adrp x16, target</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l02365" /><CodeLine lineNumber="2365"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//     add x16, x16, :lo12:target</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l02366" /><CodeLine lineNumber="2366"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//     add offset to x16 if offset != 0</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l02367" /><CodeLine lineNumber="2367"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l02368" /><CodeLine lineNumber="2368"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// add offset to x16:</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l02369" /><CodeLine lineNumber="2369"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// - abs(offset) fits 24 bits:</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l02370" /><CodeLine lineNumber="2370"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//     add/sub x16, x16, #&lt;offset&gt;&#91;, #lsl 12&#93; (up to 2 instructions)</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l02371" /><CodeLine lineNumber="2371"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// - abs(offset) does not fit 24 bits:</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l02372" /><CodeLine lineNumber="2372"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//   - offset &lt; 0:</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l02373" /><CodeLine lineNumber="2373"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//       movn+movk sequence filling x17 register with the offset (up to 4</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l02374" /><CodeLine lineNumber="2374"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//       instructions)</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l02375" /><CodeLine lineNumber="2375"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//       add x16, x16, x17</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l02376" /><CodeLine lineNumber="2376"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//   - offset &gt; 0:</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l02377" /><CodeLine lineNumber="2377"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//       movz+movk sequence filling x17 register with the offset (up to 4</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l02378" /><CodeLine lineNumber="2378"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//       instructions)</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l02379" /><CodeLine lineNumber="2379"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//       add x16, x16, x17</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l02380" /><CodeLine lineNumber="2380"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l02381" /><CodeLine lineNumber="2381"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// signing:</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l02382" /><CodeLine lineNumber="2382"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// - 0 discriminator:</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l02383" /><CodeLine lineNumber="2383"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//     paciza x16</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l02384" /><CodeLine lineNumber="2384"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// - Non-0 discriminator, no address discriminator:</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l02385" /><CodeLine lineNumber="2385"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//     mov x17, #Disc</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l02386" /><CodeLine lineNumber="2386"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//     pacia x16, x17</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l02387" /><CodeLine lineNumber="2387"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// - address discriminator (with potentially folded immediate discriminator):</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l02388" /><CodeLine lineNumber="2388"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//     pacia x16, xAddrDisc</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l02389" /><CodeLine lineNumber="2389"></CodeLine>
